#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-webauthn.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"With this, you can use link:{webauthn-test-api}/io/quarkus/test/security/webauthn/WebAuthnHardware.html[`WebAuthnHardware`]\n"
