#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-webauthn.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For this test, since we're testing both the provided callback endpoint, which updates users\n"
"in its link:{webauthn-api}/io/quarkus/security/webauthn/WebAuthnUserProvider.html[`WebAuthnUserProvider`] and the manual `LoginResource` endpoint, which deals with users\n"
"manually, we need to override the link:{webauthn-api}/io/quarkus/security/webauthn/WebAuthnUserProvider.html[`WebAuthnUserProvider`] with one that doesn't update the\n"
"`scooby` user:"
msgstr "Para este teste, como estamos testando tanto o endpoint de callback fornecido, que atualiza os usuários em seu link:{webauthn-api}/io/quarkus/security/webauthn/WebAuthnUserProvider.html[`WebAuthnUserProvider`], quanto o endpoint manual `LoginResource`, que lida com os usuários manualmente, precisamos substituir o link:{webauthn-api}/io/quarkus/security/webauthn/WebAuthnUserProvider.html[`WebAuthnUserProvider`] por um que não atualize o usuário `scooby`:"

